snippet.title: INSANITY
snippet.description:
EPIC! - http://gamejolt.com/games/insanity/94933
Creator: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCe7qX5iemAZ2CQ-Nghzo7Mg
❤ SUB 4 MOAR! ➥ http://bit.ly/IULITM
◕ My brother's channel ➥ http://bit.ly/maryogames

Insanity is a FNaF Fangame that goes all the way back to FNaF 2 and explores something that Scott mentioned, but never actually solved in the series. It will feature a small cast of antagonist characters, which allows the game to create kind of a personality for every single one of them. The game is going to be one of the scariest Fangames, since the game will have an extremely creepy ambience and moments in the game that could possibly make you a little swetty. This game will be a horror game in many ways and not only use Jumpscares to be scary.

Official Site: http://www.scottgames.com
FNAF Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/animdude

GOD BLESS YOU!
